Are you insane? Negotiation with the Sharkics? Have you forgotten [[[SPC-1258 |Japan? Burr?]]] Iberia? These may be dire times, but this is too far.

We've also killed so many of them to fuel the [[[SPC-140 |Chronicle]]]. Forgiveness will not come easily. 

It's us or them.

